#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Compare</title>"
msgstr "<title>Confronta</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; contains several compare functions: <guimenuitem>Compare by "
"Content</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> and the "
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> compare function."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; integra al suo interno diverse funzioni di confronto: "
"<guimenuitem>Confronta per contenuto</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Confronta "
"cartelle</guimenuitem> e la funzione di <link linkend=\"synchronizer"
"\">Sincronizzazione</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare by Content"
msgstr "Confronta per contenuto"

#. Tag: primary
#: compare.docbook:17 compare.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Compare</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Confronta</primary>"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Contenuto"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one file in each panel and use <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Compare by content...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &krusader; "
"will open an external graphical difference tool that is <link linkend="
"\"konfig-dependencies\">configured</link>. &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> are supported."
msgstr ""
"Seleziona un file in ciascun pannello e vai su <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Confronta per contenuto...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. &krusader; farà aprire lo strumento di confronto esterno "
"impostato in sede di <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">configurazione</"
"link>. Sono supportati &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> "
"e <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</application></"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: compare.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare Folders"
msgstr "Confronta cartelle"

#. Tag: secondary
#: compare.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Cartelle"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare the files of each panel by using <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. By "
"default newer and single files will be selected in each panel, this "
"behaviour can be changed in the <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem> "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Puoi confrontare i file contenuti nei due pannelli andando su <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Confronta cartelle</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Come impostazione predefinita, verranno selezionati i file più "
"recenti e quelli singoli. È possibile modificare questo comportamento "
"attraverso il menu <guimenuitem>Impostazioni confronto file</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files are not compared by content but by their names and dates only."
msgstr ""
"Il confronto dei file non terrà conto del loro contenuto ma soltanto del "
"nome e della data."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: compare.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Impostazioni confronto file</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configures the <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> function."
msgstr ""
"Permette di configurare la funzione <guimenuitem>Confronta cartelle</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: compare.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Select Newer and Single</guimenuitem> (default)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Seleziona più recenti e singoli</guimenuitem> (opzione "
"predefinita)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Single"
msgstr "Seleziona singoli"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Newer"
msgstr "Seleziona più recenti"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different and Single"
msgstr "Seleziona diversi e singoli"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: compare.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different"
msgstr "Seleziona diversi"

#~ msgid "Directories"
#~ msgstr "Cartelle"
